0:04:28.760,0:04:31.560
Africa, Africa!

0:04:31.560,0:04:37.880
Lord Jesus, we commit the nations of Africa into Your hands - redeem the nations,

0:04:37.880,0:04:41.760
redeem the continent of Africa, in the name of Jesus!

0:04:41.760,0:04:44.720
Redeem our leaders, in the name of Jesus!

0:04:44.720,0:04:49.320
Wherever there are troubled spots all over the world,

0:04:49.320,0:04:56.160
Father, Lord Jesus, come and rescue the nations.

0:04:56.160,0:05:00.320
All over the world, rescue the nations. There is trouble all over the world.

0:05:00.320,0:05:02.660
Father, we know with You, all things are possible.

0:05:02.660,0:05:07.040
We know with You, dry bones shall rise again.

0:05:07.040,0:05:11.800
Whatever pain, whatever area - the nations that are at war,

0:05:11.800,0:05:21.700
Father, Lord Jesus - be calm, let peace restore - unity!

0:05:21.700,0:05:24.940
I can hear breakthrough, in the name of Jesus.

0:05:24.940,0:05:27.760
Thank You, Lord!

0:05:27.760,0:05:29.980
I leave you in faith.

0:05:29.980,0:05:32.120
You will see me back in faith.

